Roles &amp; Responsibility 主要职责
? ？Provide effective HR support/consultancy to business managers including talent selection, rewards management, employee communication and relation, talent development and management, employee performance, etc.
? Collaborate across the People team and work together to introduce new employee experience initiatives that help retention of employees ？
? Lead point of contact for any employee questions or concerns across the employee life cycle, including employee relations, performance management, compensation, policy interpretation and professional development
? ？Performance Development &amp; Rewarding performance – ongoing support for business
? ？Provide advice, counsel and solutions to business leaders on people management aspects of their business including organizational, headcount planning, talent strategy, , career development, engagement, recognition and etc.
? ？Support data management, reporting and analysis - Generate HR metrics, liaise with other HR teams ？on reporting needs.
? ？HR PM: Project management of key priority operation projects across teams.
Job Requirement 工作要求 
？Education, Qualification, Work Experience 教育、资质、工作经验
? Bachelor degree or above, at least 5 years HR professional working experience, commercial organization experience is plus;
? Quick learner with the ability to handle a variety of tasks;
? Excellent command of both written and spoken English;
? Independent, creative and with a strong sense of responsibility;
? Accountable, open minded and sense of innovation;
? Able to work in the pressure and result-driven;

工作职责:
1、根据公司战略、业务发展与变化、需求，协同相关部门制定人力资源解决方案，提供专业性建议并推动实施;
2、负责多个部门的人员招聘、培训、绩效、薪酬、员工关系等人力资源工作;
3、分析部门的人员配置现状，推动业务部门完成任职资格体系及人才梯队的搭建，并持续进行优化;
4、负责部门的团队文化建设，与员工沟通互动，确保内部信息传递的通畅;
5、负责与各相关部门的沟通及关系协调，主导内部团队成员的学习、提升、培养与融合;
6、负责人力资源各项政策在各个部门的落地执行。任职资格:
1、本科及以上学历，人力资源管理等相关专业优先;
2、2年以上人力资源经理工作经验;
3、逻辑思维严谨、沟通协调能力强、具有较强的驱动力;
4、有加强的洞察能力、执行能力，能独立自主解决实际问题;
5、具备良好的团队合作意识、服务意识，积极主动;
6、有人力资源招聘实操经验，熟练掌握面试技巧，熟悉招聘渠道的开拓、维护和管理优先。
